description: O to the M to the G, the big ole baked potatoes from this truck are beautifully delicious.So all y’all hungry Houstonians better come out and try the best selection of baked potato treats that have been loaded to perfection, like the OMG 4 Meats, Smothered Pork Chop, Oxtail, Blackened Tilapia, and so much more. If you’re lookin’ for the hottest potato place on four wheels, OMG Baked Potatoes is the van for you, fo’ sho’.
name: OMG! Baked Potatoes
